node.text:
Ready to dive into the crystal blue waters off the coast and the lush green landscapes on the islands? Here are five Fijian Earth Day activities you can do right from home.
1.	Get ‘Sea Turtle Ecology’ certified 🐢
2.	Adopt a manta 🌊
3.	Tune in for turtle time 🐢
4.	Adopt a shark 🦈
5.	Become a marine biologist at home 🤿

node.text: The view is blue from this beachfront hotel in St. Barts. The stunning Le Sereno sits on a protected marine reserve where you can swim with turtles, go glass-bottom kayaking, and enjoy sunset picnics. 🌅

node.text: Turks & Caicos is truly a great spot for lounging on the beach, indulging in some truly vacation-worthy food, and experiencing a bit of luxury. ⛱☀️

node.text: At Cayo Espanto in Belize, three miles from San Pedro, there is a one-bedroom villa with custom furnishings, turquoise shutters, and a canopy bed hovering over the Western Caribbean. 🍹☀️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coastal Living on February 23, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: These rustic, overwater bungalows are two stories high, with canopy beds on the top level. Because there are only nine cabanas, the retreat in on-the-verge #BocasdelToro feels extremely intimate. Rumor has it that dolphins swim past the property and wave at visitors. ☀️🐬

node.text: If you want to have an adorable outing at the beach just let @bliss.beach do all of the work for you. You can order an Instagram-ready picnic setup just like this one straight to the beach. Available in Los Angeles, Orange County, & Palm Beach. ⛱☀️

node.text: If you want to get out of the U.S., but don't want to travel far, Bermuda is the perfect destination. Flights from NYC are just over 2 hours, and upon arrival, you'll be greeted by the island's famous pink-sand beaches and endless turquoise waters. #getaway 🌊⛵️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coastal Living on February 04, 2021. May be an image of nature, twilight and ocean.

node.text: Belize, a gorgeous slice of Central America serves up beach paradise with a side of tropical forest. Belize City, the nation's largest urban area, is perfect for active couples, who can go kayaking or snorkeling and visit the nearby Mayan sites Xunantunich and Cahal Pech or the jaguar preserve. 🤿🐠

node.text: With such lovely beaches, rainforests, and hot springs at their finger tips, Costa Rica isn’t just a rugged vacation for adventure seekers. It’s also the perfect place for a relaxing getaway. 🌴🦜
